- What?
- I'm really a fan, you see.

34
00:02:37,220 --> 00:02:38,980
Why aren't you doing any activities these days?

35
00:02:38,980 --> 00:02:43,320
Stop it, Nurse Park. Me first.

36
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:49,620
You see, my daughter is a big fan of yours.

37
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:05,670
Then everything until now was a dream?

38
00:04:04,580 --> 00:04:07,140
Oh, Mister Yoo Hyeon Jae.

39
00:04:07,140 --> 00:04:10,260
But you don't have any treatment today?

40
00:04:10,260 --> 00:04:13,560
Ah, you came for the results of yesterday's checkup?

41
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:16,600
But you need to wait a few days for it, though.

42
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,690
Yesterday?

43
00:04:18,690 --> 00:04:20,610
I came to the hospital yesterday?

44
00:04:20,610 --> 00:04:22,230
Sorry?

45
00:04:22,230 --> 00:04:27,010
Ah, yes. You came yesterday and got your treatment, you know.

46
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:30,630
