55
00:04:59,220 --> 00:05:01,860
Of course, of June.

56
00:05:01,860 --> 00:05:04,850
- 1993.
- Sorry?

57
00:05:04,850 --> 00:05:08,950
It's been a long time since 1993 has gone. It's 1994.

58
00:05:08,950 --> 00:05:11,280
1994?

59
00:05:13,420 --> 00:05:15,600
Hey.

60
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,420
Yoo Hyeon Jae died?

61
00:05:17,420 --> 00:05:18,970
Yoo Hyeon Jae,

62
00:05:18,970 --> 00:05:25,300
