Answer the phone, answer the phone.

67
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:18,920
Hello?

68
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:21,700
Gwang Jae. It's me, Yoo Hyeon Jae.

69
00:06:25,060 --> 00:06:29,020
What's with you? Why do you keep—

70
00:06:29,020 --> 00:06:30,980
You see, I...

71
