72
00:06:35,770 --> 00:06:38,120
Hey, we already made up, you know?

73
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:40,480
What? I never!

74
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:45,410
I mean, you and I... Uh, later.

75
00:06:45,410 --> 00:06:48,480
Anyway, I think you have to help me a bit.

76
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:50,890
I can't go there, so you'll have to come over here.

77
00:06:50,890 --> 00:06:55,280
Ah really, you really know how to piss someone off, don't you?

78
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:56,760
Hey, Yoo Hyeon Jae! You little—

79
00:06:56,760 --> 00:07:00,340
Gwang Jae. You're the only one who can help me now.

80
00:07:00,340 --> 00:07:06,280
Come to Bear Coffee Shop, please. I know it's shameless, but please help me out this once.

81
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:09,480
Why would I go there? Really, tsk.

82
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:13,830
Forget it, if you've got nothing better to do then wash your feet and go to sleep. Hanging up.

83
00:07:26,340 --> 00:07:30,200
Yoo Hyeon Jae? Are you in contact with Hyeon Jae, without us knowing?

84
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:32,120
No, what are you saying.

85
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:36,640
Forget it. It's fine. What were you saying?

86
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:39,320
What? Ah.

87
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:42,680
I was thinking about this while touching up the song.

88
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:47,440
It's not because I didn't have any idea, but from the start, we weren't really interested in dance or things like that,

89
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:50,660
so I was thinking about releasing a ballad album.

90
00:07:51,940 --> 00:07:55,760
Are you listening to me?

91
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:57,480
Hey, Lee Gwang Jae!

92
00:07:57,480 --> 00:08:00,150
What? Oh, yeah.

93
00:08:00,150 --> 00:08:03,830
How come no matter if Yoo Hyeon Jae is here or not, you're not interested in me whatsoever?

94
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:06,470
What are you saying?

95
00:08:06,470 --> 00:08:10,650
Hey, now our World Entertainment's figurehead is you, Park Yeong Jae.

96
00:08:10,650 --> 00:08:13,860
You're saying this now that it all fell down.

97
00:08:13,860 --> 00:08:16,640
Anyway, so this ballad album—

98
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:19,000
- I'll go out quick.
- What?

99
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,930
I'm in the middle of saying something important, where are you going?

100
00:08:20,930 --> 00:08:22,140
I'll hear you out next time, okay? Next time.

101
00:08:22,140 --> 00:08:24,290
You said I'm the figurehead.

102
00:08:24,290 --> 00:08:28,090
You're the figurehead, you are. But later. Later.

103
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:34,450
I'm sure it was a call from Hyeon Jae, though.

104
00:08:35,460 --> 00:08:39,900
These two, aren't they scheming something together?

105
00:08:43,250 --> 00:08:50,130
♫  Someone is calling me. Is it you? ♫

106
00:08:50,130 --> 00:08:56,500
♫ My heart is fluttering ♫

107
00:08:56,500 --> 00:09:02,760
♫  I'm thinking of you again today ♫

108
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:07,470
When you said you were going somewhere quick, I thought you were going to some amazing place.

109
00:09:07,470 --> 00:09:09,630
But it looks like you really just went somewhere quickly.

110
00:09:09,630 --> 00:09:13,140
I just saw you, but I'm happy to see you again.

111
00:09:13,140 --> 00:09:15,260
What are you saying, out of the blue?

112
00:09:15,260 --> 00:09:16,800
When did we see each other?

113
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:17,860
There was something like that.

114
00:09:17,860 --> 00:09:19,760
And you, really,

115
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:23,170
what's with that hair and your outfit?

116
00:09:23,170 --> 00:09:26,110
Come on, really.

117
00:09:27,850 --> 00:09:30,200
There was something like that, too.

118
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:34,840
Actually, it's good we met up. I had something to tell you anyway and was going to ask to meet up—

119
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:37,900
More than that, I have to find someone urgently.

120
00:09:37,900 --> 00:09:41,990
Who? Who do you have to find quickly?

121
00:09:41,990 --> 00:09:43,680
Yoo Hyeon Jae.

122
00:09:43,680 --> 00:09:45,110
What?

123
00:09:46,380 --> 00:09:47,640
I have to find me.

124
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:50,370
What are you saying? Are you drunk?

125
00:09:50,370 --> 00:09:55,270
That's not it. Where should I go to meet Yoo Hyeon Jae now?

126
00:09:55,270 --> 00:09:58,470
- I want to leave.
- Ah wait.

127
00:09:58,470 --> 00:10:01,870
Okay, I know it's weird.

128
00:10:01,870 --> 00:10:05,030
But you have a big network, I think you could find him right away if you look into it.

129
00:10:05,030 --> 00:10:09,110
What nonsense is that? Finding you?

130
00:10:09,110 --> 00:10:11,660
Found him! I found him, he's here, here.

131
00:10:11,660 --> 00:10:13,540
That is...

132
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:19,040
Right! That is,

133
00:10:19,040 --> 00:10:24,330
someone is going around impersonating me. Someone who looks exactly like me.

134
00:10:24,330 --> 00:10:27,660
- What?
- So please look into the places where Yoo Hyeon Jae is now.

135
00:10:27,660 --> 00:10:32,710
There will be one somewhere else, for sure. Not me, but another Yoo Hyeon Jae.

136
00:10:37,220 --> 00:10:40,910
What are they saying? I can't hear a thing.

137
00:10:55,970 --> 00:10:58,700
How did it go? Did you find him?

138
00:10:59,740 --> 00:11:04,070
It looks like there really is someone who resembles you.

139
00:11:04,070 --> 00:11:06,260
Really? Where is he, now?

140
00:11:06,260 --> 00:11:12,620
That is, it looks like he was at the studio until not long ago.

141
00:11:12,620 --> 00:11:14,710
He was working until this morning, and...

142
00:11:14,710 --> 00:11:16,120
He was working, and?

143
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:18,850
He said he had something to do in Paju.

144
00:11:18,850 --> 00:11:22,120
In Paju? Why there?

145
00:11:23,100 --> 00:11:26,330
He said he had something to do with his family.

146
00:11:26,330 --> 00:11:28,180
With his family?

147
00:11:32,530 --> 00:11:35,130
- Let me use the car.
- What?

148
00:11:40,550 --> 00:11:45,730
Ah really, I don't know why I have to be swayed around like this by you every time.

149
00:11:45,730 --> 00:11:48,870
It's because you're my sole friend, you know.

150
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:51,970
Who is your friend, uh?

151
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:10,410
- Did you forget something here?
- What?

152
00:12:12,530 --> 00:12:16,520
When did I go out from here?

153
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:17,990
You just went out.

154
00:12:17,990 --> 00:12:22,780
Did I? Then what was I doing?

155
00:12:22,780 --> 00:12:24,750
- Sorry?
- I must have been doing something, no?

156
00:12:24,750 --> 00:12:27,380
- You said you would move your parents' grave.
- What?

157
00:12:27,380 --> 00:12:32,090
You said you couldn't keep the grave anymore. That's what you said to me.

158
00:12:32,090 --> 00:12:34,180
I did?

159
00:12:35,990 --> 00:12:38,850
I did, right. Yes.

160
00:12:38,850 --> 00:12:42,720
And I didn't say where I was going, did I?

161
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:44,350
No.

162
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:55,190
Sorry, is there a lake around here, perhaps?

163
00:12:55,190 --> 00:13:00,560
A lake in the area? If you go a bit further, there is a lake called Water Lilies Lake.

164
00:13:00,560 --> 00:13:02,490
Water Lilies Lake?

165
00:13:03,900 --> 00:13:05,630
Water Lilies Lake...

166
00:13:05,630 --> 00:13:09,990
The last whereabouts of popular singer Yoo Hyeon Jae has been found.

167
00:13:09,990 --> 00:13:15,090
Yesterday afternoon, a month after his disappearance, on the side of a lake in Paju, Gyeonggi province,

168
00:13:15,090 --> 00:13:19,100
a vehicle owned by Mister Yoo Hyeon Jae has been found.

169
00:13:19,100 --> 00:13:22,010
You shouldn't go to the Water Lilies Lake.

170
00:13:22,010 --> 00:13:23,980
Thank you.

171
00:13:48,780 --> 00:13:52,950
It looks like I can't take care of you anymore.

172
00:13:53,930 --> 00:13:58,020
You wished you had lived nearby here.

173
00:14:06,180 --> 00:14:13,530
It looks like we'll be able to meet very soon, so don't be too saddened.

174
00:14:24,420 --> 00:14:26,380
This is updated news on the typhoon.

175
00:14:26,380 --> 00:14:30,550
We can say that it has completely entered the region of Seoul and Gyeonggi province, right?

176
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:31,890
